21-23 February - Miracle Soup

- 6 large onions
- 2 green peppers
- 1 large cabbage
- 1 large bunch celery
- Whole tomatoes, canned or fresh
- Season with onion soup mix or other mix

Cut vegetables in medium size pieces, cover with water and bring to a boil, simmer until soft. May be taken anytime any day. 

DIET

Day 1 Fruits except bananas. Melons preferred 
    2 Vegetables - no peas, corn, or dried beans. 1 large potato with butter
    3 Fruits and vegetables - no potatoes
    4 Bananas (6) skim milk (8 cups), soup
    5 Beef - 10-12 oz, tomatoes (6), 8 glasses of water
    6 Beef - all you want - vegetables no potato
    7 Brown rice - fruit juice - vegetables. 